# Ignore everything
*

# Don't ignore directories
!*/

!README.md

# Allow config files
!**/docker-compose.yml
!**/compose.yaml
!**/traefik.yml
!**/redis.conf

# Don't ignore .gitignore itself
!.gitignore

# Ignore secret files (these take precedence over directory allows)
.env
**/.env

# Ignore volume/data directories
**/data/
**/*data*/
**/volume*/
**/pgdata/
**/config/
**/storage/
**/logs/
**/cache/